{"tid":2438283,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"關於兼職一事想問大家","createTime":"2021-03-08T11:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T15:39:47.000Z","uid":373164,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd871693f18748f076d0694c42ba2dee1143cc3b","tid":2438283,"uid":373164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"本身返呢份工係以替工形式嘅<br />\n冇合約嘅😪<br />\n由1月17號開始返<br />\n去到1月尾 <br />\n公司同科文講話3月嘅替工每人最多返9日<br />\n咁之後到2月中<br />\n公司又改 淨係講一個替工<br />\n但就冇正式同我講呢件事<br />\n去到出3月更表 即係2月尾時候<br />\n見到我係3月完全冇更可以返<br />\n亦冇同我講過要炒我<br />\n但就踢咗我出公司群組<br />\n我想問下各位<br />\n有冇人知可以點處理？<br />\n我係可以以開工不足告間公司定點？"},{"pid":"08dc108ac35c9bdbf7829b3c2e152249c50429e5","tid":2438283,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"兼職姐 冇左咪揾過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada55861c39aa705bd5f9f5695d55845cf7e3917","tid":2438283,"uid":373164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"08dc108ac35c9bdbf7829b3c2e152249c50429e5","tid":2438283,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"兼職姐 冇左咪揾過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"其實真係冇所謂<br />\n但人人都係咁諗<br />\n咪比呢啲公司繼續蝦其他人"},{"pid":"aed687994cc472d5c7598b949418bfc7ab03114e","tid":2438283,"uid":233724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"有得用「開工不足」咁告嘅咩，岀齊糧冇拖你咪算囉 <br />\n搵下一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b720b9602bb11c8a0c2841a77865db0d8a18f412","tid":2438283,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"你過唔過418先<br />\n你又冇約"},{"pid":"412afdc44858207ff90a80198f6e22c3fb341161","tid":2438283,"uid":189068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"你都識講無合約<br />\n又無簽過每月最低工時<br />\n邊撚度有開工不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b15b91383c6aae4b9493a1d5d3345965724ebb4","tid":2438283,"uid":129676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"出得黎做野比人恰比人就預左<br />\n睇你想唔想玩野<br />\n不過都係建議拎綜援<br />\n拎左就以後唔駛比人玩<br />\n做返個人唔好做狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[綜援師]講多無謂,如果對生活唔滿意,真係唔好撚做<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2436379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2436379</a>"},{"pid":"aa471a78416f0245abfa649a9a804b0e99eb9e78","tid":2438283,"uid":118754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"睇個樣就應該係炒左你<br />\n兼職基本上話炒就炒<br />\n但又唔同你講聲又係仆街左d"},{"pid":"eaaef102d9c71179e6e853ac51593366b4f904a2","tid":2438283,"uid":118754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa471a78416f0245abfa649a9a804b0e99eb9e78","tid":2438283,"uid":118754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"睇個樣就應該係炒左你<br />\n兼職基本上話炒就炒<br />\n但又唔同你講聲又係仆街左d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:39:47.000Z","msg":"不過如果你<span class=\"xx-large\">符合418條件</span>既話就算<span class=\"xx-large\">無簽合約</span><br />\n都可以追返佢7日人工"}]}